00:22:51.890 --> 00:22:53.330
time, they grow and they change.

00:22:53.330 --> 00:22:54.330
And so-- [laughs]

00:22:54.330 --> 00:22:55.330
&gt;&gt;Leslie Chihuly: Yeah.

00:22:55.330 --> 00:22:58.100
&gt;&gt;Female Presenter: I was lucky enough to
visit the site this morning and get to see

00:22:58.100 --> 00:22:59.100
