00:23:08.869 --> 00:23:11.070
is the length of this exhibit.

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:14.090
You have the space for 30 years.

00:23:14.090 --> 00:23:19.559
And I'm wondering if that's changed at all
your thoughts on how to lay it out and how

00:23:19.559 --> 00:23:24.830
to design the exhibit because, rather than
just being there for one season, it's there

00:23:24.830 --> 00:23:25.830
for a lot longer.

00:23:25.830 --> 00:23:26.830
&gt;&gt;Dale Chihuly: Yeah.

00:23:26.830 --> 00:23:30.559
It really changed everything.

00:23:30.559 --> 00:23:36.200
We're used to having a show up for a month
or maybe three or four months.

00:23:36.200 --> 00:23:43.460
But when it's gonna be up for 30 years, you
