00:23:43.460 --> 00:23:50.000
And so, we made a lot of the glass specially
for that.

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:55.740
Like the piece that's up on the screen now,
we've done other works that have, made out

00:23:55.740 --> 00:24:02.429
of these what I call Persian parts, but all
of these are like, twice as thick as they

00:24:02.429 --> 00:24:07.850
