00:24:19.669 --> 00:24:23.100
Were there parts of the exhibit that were
inspired by the Space Needle itself?

00:24:23.100 --> 00:24:24.100
[pause]

00:24:24.100 --> 00:24:25.100
&gt;&gt;Dale Chihuly: Probably.

00:24:25.100 --> 00:24:26.100
[laughs] Yeah.

00:24:26.100 --> 00:24:28.090
&gt;&gt;Female Presenter: I noticed there were a
