00:24:28.090 --> 00:24:29.640
&gt;&gt;Dale Chihuly: I love that.

00:24:29.640 --> 00:24:30.640
&gt;&gt;Female Presenter: Yeah.

00:24:30.640 --> 00:24:36.220
&gt;&gt;Dale Chihuly: You know, there are these
